# messanger


## Installing
In both client and server directories run
``` 
npm i
npm run start
```
and you should be good to go

## Usage
First time entering the page you will be asked to enter your id or genereate a random one
![Login](/readmeAssets/login.png)

After entering id, you will be present to all your contacts and conversation on the left and the chat on 
the right.
![HomePage](/readmeAssets/typing.png)

To create a new contact, click on contacts tab and press "New Contact" button.
![Creating Contact](/readmeAssets/add-contact.png)

After adding a contact, you can create a conversation with it
![Creating Conversation](/readmeAssets/create-conversation.png)